																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "h648e38fag954cg4525g86d6g532f6aa40091",
																	"value": "An adamantine forge is very much a treasure, and any good treasure is protected by a guardian. Looks like we can defeat it with a so-called 'hot hammer'.",
