				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The party comments on reading and attempting to decipher the records of the mad drow wizard, who was one of the three looking for the Adamantine Forge.The records mention a group who located the Adamantine Forge, laying somewhere in the depth of the Underdark, and barely survived the undefeatable protector who guarded it - the adamantine golem, who has one weakness - being heated and struck by a huge forge hammer."
